lead_paragraph: Russian-born Daria Gavrilova will make her Fed Cup debut for Australia against the United States in Brisbane next week after being named in the squad for the world group playoff on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Gavrilova to Make Australia Fed Cup Debut Against U.S.
